<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payout Processed - MaalEdu Affiliate</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #7c3aed);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .payout-box {
            background-color: #faf5ff;
            border: 2px solid #8b5cf6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .payout-amount {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #8b5cf6;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .payout-details {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .payout-details p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #8b5cf6;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸ’° Payout Processed!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Your Affiliate Payout is Ready</h2>
            <p>Hi <%= affiliateName %>,</p>

            <p>Great news! Your affiliate commission payout has been successfully processed.</p>

            <div class="payout-box">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #8b5cf6; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">Payout Amount:</p>
                <div class="payout-amount">$<%= payoutAmount %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="payout-details">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #8b5cf6;">Payout Details:</h3>
                <p>
                    <span><strong>Payment Method:</strong></span>
                    <span>
                        <%= payoutMethod %>
                    </span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span><strong>Processing Date:</strong></span>
                    <span>
                        <%= processingDate %>
                    </span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span><strong>Transaction ID:</strong></span>
                    <span>
                        <%= transactionId %>
                    </span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span><strong>Commissions Earned:</strong></span>
                    <span>
                        <%= commissionsCount %> sales
                    </span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <p>Thank you for being a valued affiliate partner! Keep promoting our courses to earn more commissions.</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="https://maaledu.com/affiliate-dashboard" class="btn">View Dashboard â†’</a>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
                <strong>Note:</strong> It may take 1-3 business days for the payment to reflect in your account
                depending on your payment method.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for partnering with us!<br>The MaalEdu Affiliate Team</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <a href="https://maaledu.com" style="color: #8b5cf6;">maaledu.com</a> |
                <a href="mailto:affiliate@maaledu.com" style="color: #8b5cf6;">affiliate@maaledu.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>